<content title="School of Ministry">
  <ministry id="school">
    <name>School of Ministry</name>
    <overview>School of Ministry offers a broad perspective with
      detailed directives in order to provide the student with a
      competent education and clear vision to impact this dark
      world with the light of Christ.  Our purpose is to prepare
      and equip believers in spiritual maturity for active
      ministry roles in service to Christ. </overview> 
    <long-description>
      <p>The School of Ministry is designed to guide those who
	are seeking to serve from a practical to a professional level. Calvary
	Austin's School of Ministry offers non-credited classes for
	believers who are interested in growing in their knowledge of
	Christianity.  Classes can be taken according to individual
	interest or by a four year course plan.  The School of
	Ministry is located at Calvary Austin, 9414 Parkfield Dr.  at
	the intersection with Rundberg.</p>
